pageProduct.name: Oral B Junior Toothpaste 6+ Years Star Wars 95g
pageProduct.description:
Information

Featuring Star Wars characters and a mild flavour designed especially for kids, Oral-B Junior toothpaste helps make brushing fun.

The Sugar Shield protects against acids generated from sugars to help prevent cavities.

Developed with dentists' expertise for a healthy mouth and strong teeth with regular brushing.

Oral-B, the #1 dentist recommended toothbrush brand worldwide.

General Information

Oral-B Star Wars Junior 6+ Years Toothpaste 92g.

Oral-B® Star Wars
Junior 6+ Years

WITH SUGAR SHIELD*
*protects against acids generated from sugar
Sugar free
FLUORIDE TOOTHPASTE

Developed with dentists' expertise and kids for Healthy and Strong Teeth** **with regular brushing

Size: 92g

KEY FEATURES

• Mild mint flavour.
• Developed with dentists' expertise and kids for Healthy and Strong Teeth** **with regular brushing.
• Developed with dentists to allow children to take control of their oral health.
• Protects teeth against acids from sugars in everyday food.
• Fluoride toothpaste - sugar free

Warnings

Do not swallow. Do not use in children 6 years of age or less. Use a pea sized amount for supervised brushing to minimize swallowing. In case of intake of fluoride from other sources consult a dentist or doctor. Contains Sodium Fluoride.

CAUTION

Do not swallow.
Do not use in children 6 years of age or less.
Use a pea sized amount for supervised brushing to minimize swallowing. In case of intake of fluoride from other sources consult a dentist or doctor.

Ingredients

Water, Hydrated Silica, Sorbitol, Sodium Lauryl Sulfate, Cellulose Gum, Flavour, Trisodium Phosphate, Sodium Fluoride, Carbomer, Sodium Saccharin, Polysorbate 80, CI 77891, CI 74260.

Contains: Sodium Fluoride.

Directions

N/A
